snippet.title: Wonderbook: Walking with Dinosaurs
snippet.description:
Grab your Wonderbook™ peripheral, dig up 150-million-year-old secrets and uncover dinosaur fossils, then stand back as the prehistoric giants come to life right before your eyes.  Available November 12!

Find out more about Walking with Dinosaurs:
http://us.playstation.com/games/wonderbook-walking-with-dinosaurs-ps3.html
